reviews.text: Food is awesome but they don't have English menu tho. Affordable food with excellent quality food. Definitely worth a try
Delicious food but spaces is tight. Went for breakfast and ordered the ham and cheese croissant with chicken chop and a cup of milk tea. Be ready to order, eat and leave quickly.
The Swiss Wing is very tasty. The lunch menu has many combination and the price is cheap. Really recommend to have a try!
The restaurant is the one which get the best economic selection. You can fill your full stomach easily here with plenty of choice.
Good service and food
